&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Iguatemi&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt; População 2009: 15.222&lt;br&gt; Área: 2.947 km²&lt;br&gt; Gentílico: iguatemiense&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
